Installation Instructions
*************************

Build Dependencies
==================

- `clang` >= 3.5 or `g++` >= 4.9
- `pkg-config`
- `bison` and `flex`

Basic Installation
==================

- `git clone ...`
- `git submodule init`
- `git submodule update`
- Type `./autogen.sh`.
- Type `./configure && make`.
- Type `make check` to run tests.
- Type `make install` to install.
